      <title>厄瓜多總統下令五個省份進入緊急狀態</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/ecuador-president-decrees-state-emergency-five-provinces-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由於“內部武裝衝突”，厄瓜多爾總統丹尼爾·諾博亞週二下令五個沿海省份進入緊急狀態。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/ecuador-president-decrees-state-emergency-five-provinces-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 01:39:45 GMT</pubDate>
