      <title>俄羅斯飛彈在烏克蘭敖德薩港造成三人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russian-missile-kills-three-ukrainian-port-odesa-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[烏克蘭敖德薩港州長奧列·基佩爾表示，週三早些時候，俄羅斯飛彈襲擊造成三人死亡、三人受傷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russian-missile-kills-three-ukrainian-port-odesa-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 00:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
