      <title>烏克蘭官員與梵蒂岡特使討論被拐兒童問題</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukrainian-official-discusses-taken-children-with-vatican-envoy-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[烏克蘭總統澤倫斯基的幕僚長週二感謝梵蒂岡特使將數千名被強行帶到俄羅斯的兒童帶回家所做的努力，並請求他幫助遣返戰俘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukrainian-official-discusses-taken-children-with-vatican-envoy-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 22:13:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
